Mikrotik
/system logging action
add name=Graylog remote=<IP Graylog> remote-port=<Port Graylog> src-address=<IP Mikrotik> target=remote

Obs.: Utilizar para novos equipamentos portas acima de 5000, sendo elas 5001, 5002, 5003 â€¦

/system logging
add action=Graylog topics=critical
add action=Graylog topics=error
add action=Graylog topics=info
add action=Graylog topics=warning

 
Huawei
info-center channel 5 name loghost5
info-center channel 6 name loghost1
info-center channel 7 name loghost2
info-center channel 8 name loghost3
info-center channel 9 name loghost4

 
