info-center source arp channel 6 log level notification
info-center source arp channel 8 log level emergencies
info-center source arp channel 9 log level error
info-center loghost <IP Graylog> channel 7 port <Port Graylog>

 

OLT FURUKAWA
Nos modelos G4S, G8S, LD3032, LD3008, LW3008C, LD3016 e G2500:

syslog output info local volatile
syslog output info local non-volatile
syslog output info remote <IP Graylog>
syslog output debug remote <IP Graylog>
syslog bind-address  <IP OLT>

 

Para os modelos LD250x:    

log syslog server <IP Graylog>
